Terror tales originally published by Ace, Superior, Standard, Fawcett, Fiction House and other purveyors of comic book scares. 27 full stories, including “City of Fearful Night”, “The Deadly Diamond”, “Curse of the Werewolf”, “Jackal Man”, “Lost Child”, “The Eyeless Ones”, “Red Lightning”, “Pushing Up Daisies”, “The Vengeance Vat”, “The Accusing Fiddle”, “The Worm Turns”, “Phantom Train”, “Satan’s Bullet” and a dozen more, featuring art by Bob Powell, Bernard Baily, Sheldon Moldoff, Mike Sekowsky, Joe Certa, Manny Stallman, Warren Kremer, Howard Nostrand, Gene Fawcett, Mo Marcus, Ed Moline, Charles Nicholas, John Giunta, John Celardo and others. No fan of comic book horror can afford to miss this one. 140 standard comic book sized pages of full-story vintage reprints in black and white with color covers saddle stitched, for $29.95, from AC Comics. Printed in 2018.
